{"tid":1358962,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔好俾佢停] Beneath this HELMET is more than flesh !","createTime":"2019-07-24T04:38:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T11:36:21.000Z","uid":20948,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4e2ff46656c4cecb0ab7fbad4b627436502acfa3","tid":1358962,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:38:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港警察已經沒有維持治安保護市民嘅能力！</span></span><br />\n香港人必須要保護好自己！<br />\n<br />\n當戴頭盔 帶防具出街變成日常，我地就等於<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">成為義士嘅保護傘</span></span>！<br />\n呢兩日已經零星見到同路人戴住頭盔返工！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好俾佢停</span>！跟住落黎要行嘅路仲好長！我地要並肩作戰！<br />\n<br />\n已經有手足開始嘗試建立民安，但普通和理非市民都有機會遇上危險！<br />\n當我地大家都隨時有防具，就可以互相照應挺身而出！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">同埋！！</span></span><br />\n戴頭盔唔係淨係保護自己咁簡單，而係一個訊息！<br />\n話俾大家知，我地仲堅持緊！<br />\nWe are Hongkonger and we are everywhere!<br />\nBeneath this HELMET is more than flesh, beneath this HELMET is an idea <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">And Ideas Are Bulletproof !</span></span><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U4iDjEg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU4iDjEg.png&h=17cfd928&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">X</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f04vaLP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff04vaLP.jpg&h=74c56438&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打戴左頭盔<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wDi4fe6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwDi4fe6.png&h=7e52da5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n絲打都戴左頭盔<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ftVurmM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FftVurmM.png&h=974a8b7c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n連民主女神都戴頭盔<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7gaFx2y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7gaFx2y.png&h=4ef4dafc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n你點可以唔戴頭盔？！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上一個post：<br />\n今日已經見到有人戴頭盔返工！唔好俾佢停！香港人要保護好自己！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356750\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356750</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mxRUC1v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmxRUC1v.png&h=0ca2a98d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n我今日都戴左，希望見到你！"},{"pid":"89564b7cc8fc776aae6a5d27cc836e29f853bf0c","tid":1358962,"uid":20948,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:40:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1nwxpHZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1nwxpHZ.jpg&h=d4a4d7b0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n多謝戰友！"},{"pid":"857586cce4056e19e9399b364797b17de34df4c3","tid":1358962,"uid":273252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:44:20.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uxp3jDL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuxp3jDL.jpg&h=75ce7be0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2878f77760ccb21ebae2661a6e351fbae866ee1e","tid":1358962,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:44:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0fcb9f9cc59647942dd034cc0646fff932d66be","tid":1358962,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:48:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" c